comments: Crowder (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Allen (CLE) and does not deliver contact.
Bridges (PHX) blocks the driving shot attempt by Osman (CLE) and any contact is marginal.
Osman (CLE) makes contact to Ayton's (PHX) arm and affects his control of the ball.
Garland (CLE) makes contact to Paul's (PHX) arm during the rip-through move and not when he is in a shooting motion.
Ayton (PHX) places a hand on Osman's (CLE) body but the contact is marginal.
Booker (PHX) legally contests Markkanen's (CLE) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Rubio (CLE) makes contact to Crowder's (PHX) face before getting his hand on the ball.
Markkanen (CLE) and Ayton (PHX) engage and then quickly disengage during the inbound.
Ayton (PHX) makes contact to Allen's (CLE) arm affecting his shot attempt near the rim.
Rubio (CLE) legally contests Bridges' (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Osman (CLE) reaches in and makes contact with the ball and incidental contact with Ayton's (PHX) hand.
Okoro (CLE) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Rubio (CLE) begins falling off-balance and it is not as a result of any marginal contact by Crowder (PHX).
Crowder (PHX) briefly ties up Love (CLE) and dislodges the ball as he attempts to pass.
Rubio (CLE) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
Bridges (PHX) commits a take foul on Rubio (CLE).
Okoro (CLE) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Bridges (PHX) commits a take foul on Rubio (CLE).
Rubio (CLE) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
